Carnage/ Teltoli

* Teltoli narrowed her eyes at Cyber Claw as she circled above the clone, so 
where was this Maximal base? She looked down and noticed that Carnage was no 
longer with them, where could she have gone to?!
Teltoli swooped low and flew just above the ground, unless her friend had a 
cloaking device then she hadn't followed them this far. She sighed and began 
to fly back when suddenly she saw her friend emerge from the forest and 
begin to make her way towards the clone.
Teltoli landed beside Carnage and looked at the sludge covered reptile.
Carnage shook her hind foot and wrinkled her snout as she heard sludge 
splatter against a near by rock, she sighed and looked at Teltoli.*

Carnage: "Yuk!! Just my day, isn't it!!"

* Teltoli smiled and shook her head.*

Teltoli: "So, where were you?"

Carnage: "Well, I kinda...tripped in the swamp back there and here I 
am...the Swamp Thing!"

* Teltoli smiled and walked beside Carnage as she made her way up to the 
hill top to Cyber Claw. As the pair approached Cyber Claw Teltoli had to 
stand aside as Carnage shook the sludge from her body, not a pleasant 
experience!*
